# xetex

> Compile a PDF document from XeTeX source files
> More information: https://www.tug.org/xetex/

- Compile a PDF document:

`xetex {file value: sample.tex}`

- Compile a PDF document, specifying an output directory:

`xetex -output-directory={directory value} {file value: sample.tex}`

- Compile a PDF document, exiting if errors occur:

`xetex -halt-on-error {file value: sample.tex}`
